              </div>
            </div>
            <div
              class="flex-1 hidden bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow border-l-6 border-secondary"
            >
              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                "The team at Matranga Codeworks is incredibly skilled and easy
                to work with. They delivered on time and exceeded our
                expectations."
              </p>
              <p class="font-semibold">- Rensselaer Center for Open Source</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section id="services" class="py-32 bg-primary-400/5">
