              Stripe, never revealing their payment information. PCC
              administrators can manage the event, track donations, and download
              Excel reports at any time.
            </p>

            <p>
              Built on Google's Firebase platform, the administrators can change
              event details, turn on and off purchasing based on availability,
              and manage the event in realtime. This virtual platform
