          <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-6">
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-800">
                Soapbox Hosting
              </h3>
              <p>
                <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Soapbox</span> is my own
